","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/30973\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F30973&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07mhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=a0596e0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/30973</a> 網頁版"},{"pid":"4dbaddfeefbf1c50b13b29bf22bb0d4402b77c0d","tid":1368241,"uid":281895,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:47:02.000Z","msg":"350mb 資料<br />\n加油呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1z5x-G-QuD7cpF6jAQSRf2V1-Rjg6zopY?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1z5x-G-QuD7cpF6jAQSRf2V1-Rjg6zopY%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07mhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=1a017e39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1z5x-G-QuD7cpF6jAQSRf2V1-Rjg6zopY?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用資料說話!<br />\n<br />\n覺得中國/共產黨好, 就同佢講講<br />\n內地D司法黑暗<br />\n各種人神共憤的事<br />\n人大政協個D衰野<br />\n政府包庇惡勢力<br />\n貪污腐敗<br />\n上訪者被打 被禁錮<br />\n習近平根本唔會令中國變好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n覺得香港政府無問題, 就同佢講講<br />\n香港政府施政失誤<br />\n浪費公帑<br />\n區議會會建制錢袋<br />\n權貴不守法<br />\n利益輸送<br />\n民生困苦 (物價/數價/醫療/小店消失)<br />\n香港高官有幾廢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n覺得同意政府有D問題但應該示威者太暴力, 就比佢睇<br />\n警察最暴力一面, 尤其是無故毆打完全無衝擊掟野的人<br />\n仲有政府浪費的錢, 遠超示威者的破壞<br />\n警察各種醜惡行為及缺乏監管<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1z5x-G-QuD7cpF6jAQSRf2V1-Rjg6zopY?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1z5x-G-QuD7cpF6jAQSRf2V1-Rjg6zopY%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07mhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=1a017e39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1z5x-G-QuD7cpF6jAQSRf2V1-Rjg6zopY?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n~350MB 資料 下載<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當時事新聞咁逐樣逐樣問佢地, 問到佢地對共產黨的信心動搖, 質疑香港政權<br />\n<br />\n咁先至有 深藍變淺藍 淺藍變中立 中立變淺黃 的機會"},{"pid":"5ec50244d558461d66683082cf1c86526344ef7b","tid":1368241,"uid":266874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4dbaddfeefbf1c50b13b29bf22bb0d4402b77c0d","tid":1368241,"uid":281895,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:47:02.000Z","msg":"350mb 資料<br />\n加油呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1z5x-G-QuD7cpF6jAQSRf2V1-Rjg6zopY?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1z5x-G-QuD7cpF6jAQSRf2V1-Rjg6zopY%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07mhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=1a017e39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1z5x-G-QuD7cpF6jAQSRf2V1-Rjg6zopY?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用資料說話!<br />\n<br />\n覺得中國/共產黨好, 就同佢講講<br />\n內地D司法黑暗<br />\n各種人神共憤的事<br />\n人大政協個D衰野<br />\n政府包庇惡勢力<br />\n貪污腐敗<br />\n上訪者被打 被禁錮<br />\n習近平根本唔會令中國變好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n覺得香港政府無問題, 就同佢講講<br />\n香港政府施政失誤<br />\n浪費公帑<br />\n區議會會建制錢袋<br />\n權貴不守法<br />\n利益輸送<br />\n民生困苦 (物價/數價/醫療/小店消失)<br />\n香港高官有幾廢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n覺得同意政府有D問題但應該示威者太暴力, 就比佢睇<br />\n警察最暴力一面, 尤其是無故毆打完全無衝擊掟野的人<br />\n仲有政府浪費的錢, 遠超示威者的破壞<br />\n警察各種醜惡行為及缺乏監管<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1z5x-G-QuD7cpF6jAQSRf2V1-Rjg6zopY?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1z5x-G-QuD7cpF6jAQSRf2V1-Rjg6zopY%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07mhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=1a017e39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1z5x-G-QuD7cpF6jAQSRf2V1-Rjg6zopY?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n~350MB 資料 下載<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當時事新聞咁逐樣逐樣問佢地, 問到佢地對共產黨的信心動搖, 質疑香港政權<br />\n<br />\n咁先至有 深藍變淺藍 淺藍變中立 中立變淺黃 的機會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:37:12.000Z","msg":"唔該你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gi